        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not coding systems like <span class="text-white font-medium">NeuroGuard</span>, you can find me exploring the hiking trails of Sri Pada or researching the latest in network security.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex gap-6 mt-10">
        <a href="https://github.com/savishkanishad" class="p-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
